The paper deals with person re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves developing machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and video surveillance applications (cs.MM). The problem of open-set person re-identification also has implications for security and privacy (cs.CR) and requires advanced pattern recognition techniques (cs.AI).
